</div><div id="a18bf3443363006150239d8877e783f9" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><a name="churnprediction-modelling" class="wb_anchor"></a><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#000000;"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><b>Churn Prediction Modelling</b></span></font></span></p>
</div><div id="a18bf6e1257000f8631386649ca9a861" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p style="text-align: center;"><font color="#050505" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Modelling churn with both traditional methods and machine learning (tree models, bagging, boosting and neural networks).</span></font></p>
